Maintainer: The Chromium OS Authors <chromium-os-dev@googlegroups.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7), autotools-dev, libpam0g-dev (>= 0.72), libx11-dev, libxext-dev, libxinerama-dev, libxmu-dev, libxrandr-dev, libxt-dev, libxxf86misc-dev, libxxf86vm-dev, x11proto-core-dev
Standards-Version: 3.8.0

Package: xscreensaver
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Screen locker for Chrome OS
 Based on xscreensaver 5.08.  Modifications to lock.c and logo.c to make
 for Chrome OS.  Removed all hacks (screensaver) and kept this to a bare-minimum kit.
 Hacks can be added by adding xscreensaver-data from the main ubuntu repo.
